msgid "You have now unlocked the <Bold>Ammo Factory</> and <Bold>Ammo Depot</>.\r\n\r\n<Armed>Ship Ammo</> is produced in the <Bold>Ammo Factory</> and loaded into a ship from the <Bold>Ammo Depot</>.\r\n\r\nAs with Fuel Depots, you can link a module to an Ammo Depot and nearby tugs will automatically transport ships between them."
