msgid "Pipes will only <Bold>flow</> in <Bold>one direction</>, which can be easily seen using the <Bold>Station Status</> View (Left CTRL).\r\n\r\nYou can change the flow direction of any pipe by clicking the <Bold>flip pipe direction</> button on the pipe's popup menu, or quickly using the <Bold>H hotkey</> with any hovered or selected pipe."
