msgid "Some locations have <Bold>planet-based resources</> that you can collect, and this is accomplished by building an <Bold>Exo Planet Ops Centre</>.\r\n\r\nEach centre lets you deploy up to <Bold>4 planetary lifters</> to collect a specific resource, allowing you to fine-tune exactly which resources you want to gather.\r\n\r\nEach location only allowed a <Bold>maximum number of lifters</> in total however, so you will need to pick and choose which resources each centre will collect carefully."
